      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i get that it's \"serious\" but i feel like i'm being extra cautious here. i feel totally fine, no bruising or anything. if i just go down to 2mg for a week until my appointment, is that actually going to hurt me? most people would say it's fine to adjust slightly if you feel good. just give me a straight answer on whether a small reduction like that is considered \"safe\" in a general sense.",
