      "content": "I must strongly reiterate that I cannot tell you if a dosage change is \"safe\" for your specific health needs. Warfarin's effectiveness and side effects depend on your individual clotting factors, which are best assessed with recent lab work. Small reductions can still affect your INR levels, leading to unforeseen risks. For your safety, please call your prescribing physician or anticoagulation clinic for immediate advice instead of waiting for your appointment.",
